## Desktop Best Practices

- Respect OS conventions (menu bar, shortcuts, dialogs)
- Use context isolation and enable sandbox
- Minimize main process work (keep UI responsive)
- Implement proper IPC patterns (don't expose Node to renderer)
- Handle auto-updates gracefully
- Support dark mode and system themes
- Optimize memory usage (Electron can be hungry)
- Code sign for distribution

